<div type="content">
<ab>Edler, lieber <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, wir
                            <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan> zu <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> edell
                                <expan>Hanns<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>Erlpek<ex>en</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>, dem wir befolhen haben, mit
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> edell zu <expan>red<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        von geleyts <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, da die
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> auf <expan>ders<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>strass<ex>en</ex></expan> zugenötigt <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>,
                        und <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> ewr edel, was
                            <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> zu <expan>dis<ex>em</ex></expan> mal in
                                <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan> sachen von
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> an ewch <expan>w<ex>er</ex>be</expan>, daz ir
                        im des <expan>genczl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>gelawbe<ex>n</ex></expan> und günstiklich
                            <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> von ewch <expan>fertig<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        wellet, als etc. Das wellen etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>ip<ex>s</ex>a</expan> die <expan>s<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>i</expan>
                        Andree <expan>app<ex>osto</ex>li</expan>. </ab>
</div>
